5
00:00:54,107 --> 00:00:56,195
I think it's wise for you to allocate us a CSR budget.

6
00:00:56,195 --> 00:00:57,206
My grandma fell!

7
00:00:57,206 --> 00:00:58,206
I'm sorry.

8
00:00:58,206 --> 00:01:01,558
Because if something were to happen to you, who would I have left?

9
